metadata.name: Entrapmentalized
metadata.description:
"How can I be the man I need to be, 
when all the men I see do the same as me,
I'm caught between thoughts in this shallow cave daydreaming of peace" - DarkMythst

A representation of the depths within ourselves symbolized by 3 characters. Traveling into the mind of the artist and intended to absorb the viewer into the mythsticism of the creative exploration.


A visual abstract looping animation, last of the Illusions of Reality Series.

Soundscape by DarkMythst

Collector of this NFT will unlock both the video and 1 printable unreleased NFT of the series.
